Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.05,1:24:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}I gathered the students early that morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.55,1:24:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}I told them I would teach them for one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.56,1:24:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}The mayor asked me why.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.56,1:25:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}I said it was for my mother and for my father too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.56,1:25:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}I stood in my father's place,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.57,1:25:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}where he stood for so many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.57,1:25:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rEng}I felt sure he could hear my voice,
